channel.title: [Delta] Autospawn not spawning anything (solved)
channel.description:
I'm trying to create a shop area, but I cannot get the NPCs to spawn. I've put the code into autospawn.cfg, but not in client.java as I don't know where to put it. Using a blank delta source.
Code: Spawn = 520 2732 3471 0 0 0 0 0 1
I have not found anywhere that I can put the code into in client.java. Any help appreciated...wasn't this hard years ago, no clue why it is now.

item.title: [Delta] Autospawn not spawning anything (solved)
item.dc:creator: @tgm_clan tgm clan
item.description:
@tgm_clan wrote:

Listen closely, use this code.

spawn(space)=(space)520(tab)X(tab)Y(tab)floor(tab)0(tab)0(tab)0(tab)0(tab)0(tab)1

Common sense : Delete the (tab) and put a actual tab, same for the

(space)
